{"tid":1614342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立 Hong Kong Independence","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T07:11:11.000Z","uid":199727,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"66b6d72a01ff5dcd44c14c8b232750596b6c6d16","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"香港人已毫無退路。<br />\n<br />\n面對共產黨血腥鎮壓，無底線打壓異己。<br />\n香港人已無法相信一國兩制，只剩下香港獨立一條路。<br />\n<br />\n政黨政客再與港獨割席只是自私及短視的舉動，他們與港獨割席，希望政黨利益能在這個不合法政權中維持，並在槍火下向共產黨乞討基本公民權利，極之荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n面對極權，港人只能逆境自強，提起頭堅持在街巷上奮戰，直至共產黨向香港人投降。共產黨將成為這一代及下一代的夢魘。追求香港獨立，只為爭取港人重奪主權，不再遭受中共無理壓迫，守護「香港人」的珍貴身份及文化。<br />\n<br />\n請支持香港獨立 Hong Kong Independence <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/37419310_10160484395850265_5577314844048097280_o_0u156_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F37419310_10160484395850265_5577314844048097280_o_0u156_1200x0.png&h=5f6f18fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1bd6905792d2f4a8deb0956926d9038fb08e94b","tid":1614342,"uid":77132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3SSbqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3SSbqe.png&h=4e5eb57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲住公屋俾人睇唔起啦快啲投身警察啦"},{"pid":"fe44201342592384b419ce6d65686f0136e8231f","tid":1614342,"uid":303052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZ1GPbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZ1GPbN.jpg&h=2767630d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8qo2wQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8qo2wQ.gif&h=e9ecabc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf720f31cd3820c7595d3d5fcd2e9eef328608b4","tid":1614342,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:10:28.000Z","msg":"【和勇合一，遍地開花戰略】大家要全民升級，就去政府合署度讀臨時議會宣言！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nThis way, sir"},{"pid":"f61aab2f007ee1ce104baa005877d61454d05f42","tid":1614342,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"真普選=香有實然主權治權=自治=獨立<br />\n<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"359a6bc3f192910c95689156f7ac523a73f3ce6a","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"你認為除咗港獨之外有出路既歡迎提出<br />\n我絕對唔會割席，亦都請你唔好割我席。"},{"pid":"7a3ed4d915d39e0a1770186ba599d469b75eac7f","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"無謂再用香港自治既字眼去自欺欺人<br />\n你要雙普選，佢用實彈射你。<br />\n你要香港自治，佢又係用實彈射你。<br />\n你要香港獨立，佢都係用實彈射你。"},{"pid":"227be0d7addd512bd57fa57f74571a75eafec2af","tid":1614342,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"d58b0a11fcf563a7c26bf1d8481efdc1d31f5c24","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:16:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立，大勢所趨。<br />\n驅遂共黨，光復香港。"},{"pid":"732a728d412db1cab9318481723c8052e274ae77","tid":1614342,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:17:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"913505199d5aa8ddcc4aac859668e12b7e30e484","tid":1614342,"uid":227699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359a6bc3f192910c95689156f7ac523a73f3ce6a","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"你認為除咗港獨之外有出路既歡迎提出<br />\n我絕對唔會割席，亦都請你唔好割我席。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:17:38.000Z","msg":"唔好係連登鳩嗌,整多兩張文宣落街貼連儂牆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a2d01988221a351ebf01d5c867f811a668c51c","tid":1614342,"uid":199727,"li